  "signal_description": "Calculate the average approval time for timesheet records and display it along with the project manager. The query is performed on the 'defaultview-197' table. The 'ApprovalTimeCalculation' subquery flattens the table and calculates the average approval time by subtracting the first end time of the 'Create Timesheet Record' event from the current end time, grouped by the timesheet record. The outer query filters the results to include only the 'Approve Timesheet Record' and 'Auto-Approve Timesheet Record' events. The results are ordered by the average approval time in descending order."
